Build 20011204

From the resource perpsective, I went to look at the build path for a Java 
project.  I got an error saying the JDT UI plugin could not start, with the 
following in the log.
I have not posted this to eclipse-dev, since it sounds like this one was 
mentioned in todays arch call.

I had just relaunched from having accidentally shut down my machine, so Eclipse 
may not have exited normally before.
